OL,3,CChurch of England to apologise for
OL,4,Crole in historical forced adoptions
OL,6,FThe Church of England is to apologise
OL,7,Ffor its role in historical forced
OL,8,Fadoptions, ITV News Social Affairs
OL,9,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker and Senior
OL,10,FProducer Lottie Kilraine report
OL,12,FThe Church of England is planning to
OL,13,Fissue an apology for its role in the
OL,14,Fpractice of historical forced
OL,15,Fadoption, ITV News understands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
