SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775682667
OL,3,CChurch of England to apologise for
OL,4,Crole in historical forced adoptions
OL,6,FDr Michael Lambert, from Lancaster
OL,7,FUniversity, told ITV News the Church
OL,8,Fof England was the significant player
OL,9,Fin historic forced adoptions, second
OL,10,Fonly to the state
OL,12,F"Hearing from the institution that
OL,13,Fthey in fact did nothing wrong will
OL,14,Fmean a great deal," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
