OL,3,CChurch of England to apologise for
OL,4,Crole in historical forced adoptions
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer said 'his instinct'
OL,7,Fis to issue a government apology for
OL,8,Fthe state's role in the forced
OL,9,Fadoption scandal, in an exclusive
OL,10,Finterview with ITV News last week
OL,12,FThe damning report comes after an
OL,13,Fongoing ITV News investigation has
OL,14,Flaid bare the trauma and neglect faced
OL,15,Fby both mothers and their children,
OL,16,Fnow adults, many of whom are still
OL,17,Fsearching for answers or have since
OL,18,Fdied.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
